      "_type": "text",
      "contents": "\n\n  "
    },
    {
      "_type": "sentence",
      "contents": "Axiom surf : idpath base = idpath base.",
      "messages": [],
      "goals": []
    },
    {
      "_type": "text",
      "contents": "\n\n  "
    },
    {
      "_type": "sentence",
      "contents": "Definition TwoSphere_ind (P : TwoSphere -> Type)\n    (b : P base) (s : idpath b = transport2 P surf b)\n    : forall (x : TwoSphere), P x\n    := fun x => match x with base => fun _ => b end s.",
      "messages": [],
      "goals": []
    },
    {
      "_type": "text",
      "contents": "\n\n  "
    },
    {
      "_type": "sentence",
      "contents": "Axiom TwoSphere_ind_beta_surf : forall (P : TwoSphere -> Type)\n    (b : P base) (s : idpath b = transport2 P surf b),\n    apD02 (TwoSphere_ind P b s) surf = s @ (concat_p1 _)^.",
      "messages": [],
      "goals": []
    },
    {
      "_type": "text",
      "contents": "\n\n"
    },
    {
      "_type": "sentence",
      "contents": "End TwoSphere.",
      "messages": [],
      "goals": []
    },
    {
      "_type": "text",
      "contents": "\n\n(* ** The non-dependent eliminator *)\n\n"
    },
